# HG changeset patch
# User Brian Grinstead <bgrinstead@mozilla.com>
# Parent  e90ab0faff54a4a7f6e0d9a840e5c8adf4a60606
Bug 1392352 - Part 1 - Remove extra tabbrowser-tabbox binding

This is used to change one property on the tabbox, which can be done
instead by passing an option into the tabbox.

